    Registrar recorded it as Hill Place, and there is an old map showing it as Hill&#39;s Place. We know this is the correct street,
    because we can check by following the enumerators&#39; footsteps from house to house until we reach adjacent and nearby streets
    within each census. Anyway, here is the transcription, warts and all.
</p>
